{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"0781e4beea","title":"在中共中央政治局常委会上的讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"f2de44ab21","index":0,"year":1935,"month":9,"day":20,"articleId":"0781e4beea"}],"tags":[{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji7-2","name":"毛泽东全集第7卷(2)","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji7-2.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji7-2":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"3a0af016d7","type":"paragraph","text":"在中共中央政治局常委会上的讲话！","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"0781e4beea"},{"id":"aeb2402400","type":"paragraph","text":"（1935年9月20日）","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"0781e4beea"},{"id":"917978fff7","type":"paragraph","text":"组织部应该调查了解干部，要了解连以上干部。我们现在只了解高级干部，中下级干部还不了解。为了巩固部队，需要了解干部：为了扩大干部，需要支配干部：为了与反革命作斗争，需要了解干部的一些倾向问题。组织部需要了解下层情形，这是组织部的主要工作。要把教育工作包括在组织工作之内。此外，对地方工作，组织部也应该给予帮助","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"0781e4beea"},{"id":"00e43482a4","type":"paragraph","text":"“编余”二字不大好。对于一些工作上需要的，就是编制上没有，也应该写上。我们应该承认，过去对干部的优待不够。现在的干部是精华，应该注意保护","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"0781e4beea"},{"id":"f1d5338c73","type":"paragraph","text":"[1]1935年9月20日，中共中央政治局常委会在岩昌县哈达铺召开。本篇一是毛泽东在讨论组织部工作问题时讲话的一部分：本篇二是毛泽东关","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"0781e4beea"}],"page":{"id":"6360c6587f","publicationId":"maoquanji7-2","articleId":"0781e4beea","start":234,"end":234}}}},"__N_SSG":true}